    "is_free": true,
    "description": "运用各式武器、枪械及魂卡一路鏖战，找到回家的路。捕捉恶魔，在战斗中将其作为盟友召唤出来，共同挑战地狱女王。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/8bfb67881622a4aa007b1c43146ac08e.poster.avif?t=1728962518\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/8bfb67881622a4aa007b1c43146ac08e.webm?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/8bfb67881622a4aa007b1c43146ac08e.mp4?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你是一名猎魔人，在地狱中迷失了方向，被意外传送到了这片恶魔的领地。现在，你必须和你的盟友们团结一致，寻找那把神秘的钥匙，开启通往原世界的传送门。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>使用恶魔灵魂畅爽砍杀</strong><br>将每一只遇到的恶魔都收入囊中，让它们在战斗中成为你的盟友，同时解锁各式枪械和武器来进行射击和斩杀。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/16a575b7dde0ac19ae3f196d3f3fc183.poster.avif?t=1728962518\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/16a575b7dde0ac19ae3f196d3f3fc183.webm?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/16a575b7dde0ac19ae3f196d3f3fc183.mp4?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>破盾与封印</strong><br>打出组合攻击，击破敌人的护盾，把它们的灵魂封入魂卡，纳入你的牌组中。冒险途中遇到的每一位敌人都有可能化为你手中的恶魔灵魂。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/a14c662f6cb0644d1933e141c6fa0032.poster.avif?t=1728962518\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/a14c662f6cb0644d1933e141c6fa0032.webm?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/a14c662f6cb0644d1933e141c6fa0032.mp4?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>构建自己的魂卡组</strong><br>在开始猎魔人任务之前，先构建一个符合你喜好的恶魔灵魂卡组吧。有超过100种魂卡可供选择，无论你喜欢何种游戏风格，都可以找到自己的玩法。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/56cfa71bf2e9cd66a199d83395ebe5a3.poster.avif?t=1728962518\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/56cfa71bf2e9cd66a199d83395ebe5a3.webm?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/56cfa71bf2e9cd66a199d83395ebe5a3.mp4?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/d107b27751ef4bc9b1e010319fc2ce9e.avif?t=1728962518\" width=616 height=168 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>探索美丽的地狱世界</strong><br>踏入这片充满生机和故事的2D像素风世界，探索地狱中的多样地域，展开一段惊心动魄的冒险。从风景如画的海滩到熔岩流淌的火山堡垒，再到郁郁葱葱的森林，更多神奇的地方正等着你去发现。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/5690bdcb2e4a28a700d0125ab929138f.poster.avif?t=1728962518\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/5690bdcb2e4a28a700d0125ab929138f.webm?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/5690bdcb2e4a28a700d0125ab929138f.mp4?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>和朋友一起猎魔</strong><br>单打独斗太过危险，不如插入另一只手柄，邀请你的朋友一起加入本地合作模式的冒险之旅吧。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/f3a2c93adf654b027ca90b6b62fef551.poster.avif?t=1728962518\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/f3a2c93adf654b027ca90b6b62fef551.webm?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/f3a2c93adf654b027ca90b6b62fef551.mp4?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>尽情享受地狱中的每一刻</strong><br>在繁重的任务间隙玩点轻松的小游戏。约会、钓鱼、植树、帮助当地冒险者，还能接受各种支线任务。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/e36cac9634da5834465ae1a2393d05c2.poster.avif?t=1728962518\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/e36cac9634da5834465ae1a2393d05c2.webm?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187350/extras/e36cac9634da5834465ae1a2393d05c2.mp4?t=1728962518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
